<subSubSection pageId="227" pageNumber="832" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="227.[2066,2659,880,1308]" pageId="227" pageNumber="832">
Placement of R. ranjiniaein 
<taxonomicName box="[2463,2547,998,1032]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Rattus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="227" pageNumber="832" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Rattus</taxonomicName>
is unresolved, and it has not been included in any phylogenetic studies. This unique species should eventually be included in different genus. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
